docs {
  ## Create Experiment - STT (V1)

  Creates an STT (Speech-to-Text) experiment. Models are string arrays.
  Requires `voice_input_column` pointing to the column containing audio input.
  model_params include STT-specific fields: num_speakers, diarization_threshold, booleans, dropdowns.

  ### Response
  ```json
  {"message": "Experiment created successfully.", "status": 200}
  ```
}
